nses, which will not be replaced under any circumstances.<br/><br/>This warranty does not cover damage caused by accidents (impact, crushing, scratching, etc.), improper or unauthorized use of the frame, unauthorized alterations, repairs or tampering. Any damage not covered under warranty can be repaired for a charge after verification.</p><p>Should a defect occur, please send your frame(s) and include your name, phone number, mailing address, email address, to: </p><p>L’Écurie Paris distribution<br/>1065 La Mirada Ct, Vista, CA 92081<br/>United States<br/>Email: experience@lecurieparis.com</p>",
